title: MSAR
description: The MSAR is overpriced for a book you will only use once. I found all my MCAT study materials online and I was able to score a 33 but nowhere could I find a copy of the MSAR. I photographed most of the relevant pages, including the admission requirements for the US medical schools. If you appreciate my work, please donate via bit coin at 1AEUdwB7XgbcYUBuHLtCkDF74hbRkyfLW. For every dollar I received I will transcribe a page to a searchable format. Thank you and good luck getting into medical school!
